      <h1 class='title'>General Commissioners: Amalgamation of Divisions</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='lords-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HL Deb 24 January 2005 vol 668 cc45-6WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_46ws' title='Col. 46WS &mdash; HL Deb 24 January 2005 vol 668 c46WS' name='column_46ws' href='#column_46ws' rel='bookmark'>46WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0668P0-05410'>
        <a name='S5LV0668P0_20050124_LWS_6'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-catherine-ashton' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0668P0_20050124_LWS_6' title='Link to this speech by Ms Catherine Ashton' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-catherine-ashton" title="Ms Catherine Ashton">The Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State, Department for Constitutional Affairs (Baroness Ashton of Upholland)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S5LV0668P0-05410">On 20 January 2005 I made an order under Section 2(6) of the <a href="/acts/taxes-management-act-1970">Taxes Management Act 1970</a> amalgamating the Saffron Walden and West Essex divisions in Essex with effect from 24 January 2005.</p><p id="S5LV0668P0-05411">The amalgamation was made at the request of the general commissioners in the divisions with the aim of improving the organisational efficiency of the divisions. I have placed a copy of the order amalgamating the divisions in the Libraries of both Houses.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
